summary: Totally tripped at work today (cause that’s how my life is going) because I was chasing a toddler who was chasing a puppy and...
body: Totally tripped at work today (cause that’s how my life is going) because I was chasing a toddler who was chasing a puppy and the sting of the scrape was nothing to shame of knowing there was 3 parents and 2 grandparents there. Plus all the little kids. But then I remembered that Brie Larson did not make a whole movie about getting back up after we fall for me to succumb to crippling social shame. So I just jumped up and did a pose and said “I’m ok!” And I know this isn’t what Captain Marvel was intended to empower but hey, I’m taking it as my empowering moment today.
